DFK-01.details: The TorqueFlite® 8 eight-speed automatic transmission operates in eight gears for quality control and excellent performance in all conditions.

DMD-01.details: A numerically lower axle ratio results in lower engine rpm and better fuel economy.  A numerically higher ratio improves acceleration, climbing grades, carrying loads or pulling a trailer.

ERB-01.details:
This award-winning Pentastar® V6 engine delivers up to 305 horsepower and 269 pound-feet of torque. It features a compact, lightweight design with dual overhead camshafts, 24 valves, high-flow intake and exhaust ports, Variable Valve Timing and Electronic Throttle Control. The engine gets up to 17 city / 25 highway mpg[1] and has a maximum towing capacity of 7,600 pounds[2].

2. When properly equipped. See dealer for details.

1. Manufacturer estimated mpg with 3.6L engine and eight-speed automatic transmission, 4X2. Actual mileage may vary.

2. When properly equipped. See your dealer for details.

ERC-02.details:
The 3.6L Pentastar® V6 engine has up to 295 horsepower and 260 pound-feet of torque and features a compact, lightweight design with dual overhead camshafts, high-flow intake and exhaust ports, Variable Valve Timing and Electronic Throttle Control with integrated speed control. It also includes Engine Stop/Start (ESS) Technology. The 3.6L Pentastar® engine and eight-speed automatic transmission can get up to 19 city / 26 highway mpg[1] and tow up to 6,200 pounds[2].

1. EPA estimated mpg with 3.6L engine and eight-speed automatic transmission, RWD. Actual mileage may vary.

2. When properly equipped. See dealer for details.

EXF-01.details:
The 3.0L EcoDiesel V6 engine delivers 240 horsepower and 420 lb-ft of torque. It has a maximum towing capacity of 9,200 pounds[1].

1. When properly equipped. See dealer for details.

EZH-01.details:
The 5.7-liter V8 HEMI engine delivers 395 horsepower and 410 pound-feet of torque. The engine gets up to 14 city / 20 highway mpg[1] and has a maximum towing capacity of 10,620 pounds[2].

1. When properly equipped. See dealer for details. Manufacturer estimated mpg with 5.7L engine and eight-speed automatic transmission, 4X2. Actual mileage may vary.

2. When properly equipped. See your dealer for details.

GT6-01.description: Power Heated Mirrors with Manual Fold-Away

GXM-01.details: Remote keyless entry locks and unlocks the doors and tailgate of your vehicle at the touch of a button on your key fob. You can also activate the panic alarm on the fob. The AllSecure® Central Locking System engages your vehicle's theft deterrent system to help protect your entire vehicle. The system even protects the contents of the available RamBox® Cargo Management System.

H7-01.details: The cloth low-back bucket seats are designed to keep you firmly planted during spirited driving.

JLP-01.details: The GPS Antenna Input allows a clear GPS signal inside the vehicle.

JP8-01.details: Fine-tune the comfort of your seats with the manual adjust feature, which lets you move the seat to your preferred position.

JPY-01.description: Power Windows with Front One-Touch-Down Feature

MRU-01.details: The black tubular side steps look great and fit the rocker panels snugly. They include molded end caps to accent your truck's styling and a wide skid-resistant stepping surface for easy entry and exit.

MZR-01.details: The 3.0L EcoDiesel badge identifies the engine at a glance.

NHD-01.details: The heavy-duty transmission oil cooler maintains the transmission at the optimal temperature for it to operate during towing and other demanding tasks.

NHE-01.details: The engine oil heat exchanger helps regulate the temperature of the 5.7L HEMI® V8 engine, when pulling heavy loads.

NMC-01.details: The heavy-duty engine cooling system is designed to vent excess heat generated by heavy engine use.

NZD-01.details: The next-generation engine controller is a powertrain controller consolidating both engine and automatic transmission controllers into one component. It provides better coordination between engine and transmission functions for excellent performance and efficiency.

RA2-01.details:
Uconnect® 3 includes a 5-inch display, AM/FM radio, available SiriusXM® Satellite Radio[1] with one year of service, Bluetooth® Streaming Audio, Voice Command, Hands-Free Calling[2] and Voice Text Reply[3] (not compatible with iPhone® mobile devices).

1. SiriusXM services require subscriptions, sold separately after the 12-month trial included with the new vehicle purchase. If you decide to continue your service at the end of your trial subscription, the plan you choose will automatically renew and bill at then-current rates until you call SiriusXM at 1-866-635-2349 to cancel. Trial service is not transferrable or refundable. See SiriusXM Customer Agreement for complete terms at www.siriusxm.com. All fees and programming subject to change. Satellite service is available only to those at least 18 and older in the 48 contiguous USA and D.C. Internet radio service is available throughout satellite service area and in AK and HI with limited coverage.

2. The Uconnect® Phone requires a mobile phone equipped with the Bluetooth® Hands-Free Profile. To check phone compatibility please visit UconnectPhone.com.

3. Voice Text Reply feature requires a compatible mobile device enabled with Bluetooth® Message Access Profile (MAP). iPhone® and some other smartphones do not currently support Bluetooth MAP. Visit www.UconnectPhone.com for system and device compatibility. Ensure MAP is ON and incoming message notification is enabled. Also requires the use of a compatible smartphone that supports text messaging and Bluetooth.

RSD-02.description: SiriusXM® Sat Radio w/ 1-Yr Radio Subscription
RSD-02.details:
New vehicles that are equipped with SiriusXM® Satellite Radio[1] come with a 12-month All Access trial subscription. Rock every channel available in your vehicle including all of the premium programming. That's 12 months of commercial-free music, plus sports, news, talk and comedy-it's the freedom of over 150 channels to enjoy from coast to coast. And SiriusXM streaming is included with your All Access trial subscription, so now you can listen online, on the SiriusXM app and on connected devices. You can even customize your favorite music and comedy channels and listen to shows on demand. Certified Pre-Owned vehicles come with a 3-month All Access trial.

1. SiriusXM services require subscriptions, sold separately after the 12-month trial included with the new vehicle purchase. If you decide to continue your service at the end of your trial subscription, the plan you choose will automatically renew and bill at then-current rates until you call SiriusXM at 1-866-635-2349 to cancel. Trial service is not transferrable or refundable. See SiriusXM Customer Agreement for complete terms at www.siriusxm.com. All fees and programming subject to change. Satellite service is available only to those at least 18 and older in the 48 contiguous USA and D.C. Internet radio service is available throughout satellite service area and in AK and HI with limited coverage.
